flowchart LR
    A[Agent messages<br/>from context] --> B[transformContext hook chain]
    B --> C{Modified messages}
    C --> D[convertToLlm<br/>default or overridden]
    D --> E[LLM messages<br/>provider format]
    E --> F[before_provider_request<br/>hook]
    F --> G[Provider request<br/>HTTP]
    G --> H[LLM response]
    H --> I[streamAssistantResponse<br/>events]
    I --> J[executeToolCalls<br/>if tool calls]
    J --> K[Tool results]
    K --> L[turn_end]
    L --> M{check steering}
    M -->|steering| N[inner loop continues<br/>inject steering]
    M -->|no steering| O[check follow-up]
    O -->|follow-up| P[outer loop continues]
    O -->|none| Q[agent_end]

    subgraph Hooks
        B
        F
    end

    style Hooks fill:#e1f5e1